repository-code: "https://github.com/jbellsolutions/forge"
url: "https://github.com/jbellsolutions/forge"
abstract: >
  forge is a Python SDK for building agent systems decoupled from any single
  model provider. It implements an 8-layer harness — kernel, memory, tools,
  healing, swarm, skills, use-case, observability — with provider-as-profile
  YAML adapters, full-fidelity trace persistence, eval-gated skill autosynthesis,
  topology × consensus swarm primitives, and a recursive self-modification loop
  honoring the AutoAgent regularizer.
